WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.897
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.184 --> 01:37.868
=Episode 3=

01:45.456 --> 01:46.416
(Gongshu Yang,
Magistrate of Jingzhao Prefecture)

01:46.416 --> 01:47.056
Magistrate Gongshu.

01:56.944 --> 01:58.544
(Yuan Fang, Military Governor of Huaixi)

02:21.896 --> 02:22.416
Yes.

02:25.176 --> 02:25.696
Your Majesty.

02:27.696 --> 02:28.217
Your Majesty.

02:28.856 --> 02:29.896
I deserve death.

02:31.657 --> 02:35.217
I picked up Military Governor Yuan
in the capital outskirts some days ago.

02:35.537 --> 02:36.416
But unexpectedly,

02:36.977 --> 02:39.097
assassins followed immediately after.

02:39.221 --> 02:40.217
(Gao Wenhuan)

02:40.217 --> 02:42.176
They abducted Military Governor Yuan.

02:42.416 --> 02:45.456
I sent men searching tirelessly
for two days,

02:45.537 --> 02:47.176
and finally found him

02:47.696 --> 02:48.616
in a rundown shack

02:48.977 --> 02:50.176
in the capital outskirts.

02:50.616 --> 02:51.456
But

02:51.456 --> 02:53.937
h-he is dead.

02:54.456 --> 02:55.257
You...

02:55.257 --> 02:57.817
I have already reported this
to the Jingzhao Prefecture.

03:06.097 --> 03:06.696
Your Majesty,

03:07.497 --> 03:09.657
with Military Governor Yuan dead,

03:09.736 --> 03:12.657
Huaixi has become paramount.

03:14.497 --> 03:17.136
The Huaixi weaponry case
is critical to me.

03:17.817 --> 03:19.416
I am about the age to reign the nation,

03:19.777 --> 03:22.016
but the Marquis Muyang
and his faction obstruct me.

03:23.217 --> 03:25.016
Mother's stance remains ambiguous.

03:26.977 --> 03:28.377
He's highly trusted by Mother,

03:28.896 --> 03:31.016
quite influential at court.

03:31.817 --> 03:34.937
Only a major offense
can shake his foundation.

03:35.817 --> 03:38.416
The Marquis Muyang smuggles
our nation's blades and crossbows

03:38.576 --> 03:41.016
to Cangbei for personal profit.

03:41.537 --> 03:44.217
Even the Empress Dowager
could not pardon such a crime.

03:44.616 --> 03:45.416
Indeed.

03:46.097 --> 03:48.257
Thus, she hasn't hindered
the investigation,

03:49.377 --> 03:51.097
but I need concrete evidence.

03:51.657 --> 03:53.232
But with Military Governor Yuan dead,

03:53.232 --> 03:55.097
the evidence is also likely gone.

03:56.657 --> 03:58.217
The urgent task now

03:58.896 --> 04:01.777
is to prevent the Marquis Muyang's men
from infiltrating Huaixi.

04:02.016 --> 04:04.817
Otherwise, the weaponry case
could never be solved.

04:06.416 --> 04:08.240
As long as Marquis Muyang
isn't eliminated,

04:08.697 --> 04:12.056
my path to reigning the nation
will only be fraught with difficulties.

04:12.376 --> 04:13.176
Your Majesty,

04:13.897 --> 04:15.457
you must plan early.

04:17.457 --> 04:19.137
(Yuan Fang is dead now.)

04:19.496 --> 04:22.856
(Huaixi needs a capable replacement.)

04:30.256 --> 04:32.457
Today is the birthday
of Emperor Immortal.

04:32.777 --> 04:34.217
Master said

04:34.217 --> 04:36.496
to enhance the fortune
of your lamp today.

04:41.017 --> 04:42.657
Mrs. Lv was offering her lamp just now?

04:43.217 --> 04:44.217
Exactly.

04:44.537 --> 04:47.176
Yesterday, she made a scene
about the size of her lamp.

04:47.496 --> 04:49.936
Just now, she insisted on placing hers
on the highest tier.

04:50.457 --> 04:51.897
What kind of place is this?

04:52.176 --> 04:54.777
The highest tier is only for royalty.

04:54.856 --> 04:55.936
How dare she do so?

04:56.256 --> 04:57.616
What happened in the end?

04:58.056 --> 05:00.176
Her lamp is put
in the center of the second tier.

05:04.056 --> 05:05.496
(Tianqiong Hall)
God of Literature shines upon destiny.

05:05.496 --> 05:07.496
They say this Master Ye
is very efficacious.

05:07.577 --> 05:09.376
Gold palace and platform.

05:13.056 --> 05:13.856
Vermilion steps...

05:14.056 --> 05:15.296
- Master, it's our turn.
- Master, it's our turn.

05:15.296 --> 05:15.936
- Our turn.
- Our turn.

05:15.936 --> 05:16.897
Master Ye.

05:19.176 --> 05:19.856
You're here.

05:20.336 --> 05:22.296
Come on. You can pick one lamp

05:22.296 --> 05:24.097
from what we have here.

05:24.097 --> 05:25.736
We have the Seven Stars Lamp

05:25.736 --> 05:26.897
and Jiuyao Everlasting Lamp.

05:27.697 --> 05:28.816
What's the difference?

05:29.137 --> 05:30.577
The Jiuyao Everlasting Lamp

05:30.577 --> 05:32.137
resembles an eternal lamp.

05:32.137 --> 05:33.977
Primarily, it wards off calamities.

05:33.977 --> 05:36.137
The Seven Stars Lamp
is for making wishes to the gods.

05:36.856 --> 05:37.616
How to make wishes?

05:38.137 --> 05:40.816
Write your wish on the lamp,

05:41.017 --> 05:42.856
then place it on my wooden stand

05:42.856 --> 05:44.897
and consecrate it for eighty-one days.

05:44.897 --> 05:46.176
Then cast it into the Han River,

05:46.496 --> 05:49.296
and it will float up to the sky
along with the current.

05:49.697 --> 05:52.577
Once Emperor Immortal sees it
and he will grant your wish.

05:54.376 --> 05:55.657
That sounds quite fascinating.

05:56.056 --> 05:57.777
Master, I wish for my son

05:57.777 --> 05:59.457
to have a smooth official career.

05:59.457 --> 06:00.577
Okay. Please wait a moment.

06:00.577 --> 06:01.217
Come on.

06:01.217 --> 06:02.256
It's my turn now.

06:02.736 --> 06:03.577
Master.

06:03.577 --> 06:04.577
Hurry up.

06:04.577 --> 06:05.137
Okay.

06:05.376 --> 06:06.457
I can't wait.

06:06.457 --> 06:07.017
Come on.

06:07.137 --> 06:07.736
Ready now.

06:09.296 --> 06:11.312
Your Highness,
the brush, ink, and paper are here.

06:12.577 --> 06:14.777
Please write the name
of the blessed person

06:14.856 --> 06:16.256
on the bottom of the lamp.

06:16.537 --> 06:18.256
Then select a position to place it.

06:18.936 --> 06:20.496
Does it have to be the real name?

06:20.697 --> 06:21.777
Of course.

06:22.697 --> 06:24.217
What if there are two names?

06:25.176 --> 06:27.296
Then use the name given at birth

06:27.296 --> 06:28.736
and kept in the ancestral temple.

06:35.816 --> 06:36.337
(Jingzhao Prefecture)
Make way!

06:36.337 --> 06:37.856
Please don't make it difficult for me.

06:37.856 --> 06:38.376
General Lu.

06:38.457 --> 06:39.616
- No way!
- Stop it!

06:39.616 --> 06:40.400
(Lu Changfu,
General of the Imperial Guard)

06:40.897 --> 06:42.416
Magistrate Gongshu.

06:44.697 --> 06:46.217
Why are you here?

06:46.616 --> 06:48.376
If Yuan Fang is alive,
he belongs to Huaixi.

06:48.376 --> 06:50.296
If dead, the Imperial Guard
should take charge.

06:50.296 --> 06:52.537
Do you guys in Jingzhao Prefecture
have nothing to do?

06:52.777 --> 06:54.616
Do not force me to use force.

06:54.977 --> 06:56.577
Bring out Yuan Fang's body!

06:58.577 --> 07:01.376
Lord Lv, you intend to meddle in this?

07:02.777 --> 07:03.616
I wouldn't dare.

07:04.137 --> 07:06.137
I merely happened upon General Lu

07:06.816 --> 07:08.056
and came to supervise.

07:08.056 --> 07:09.256
Enough talk with him.

07:10.337 --> 07:13.457
Military Governor Yuan had received
the imperial decree to inspect Huaixi,

07:13.657 --> 07:15.337
but he died suddenly while returning.

07:15.657 --> 07:16.736
While, Marquis Muyang

07:16.897 --> 07:19.496
bears a blood relation
to the prominent Zhou family in Huaixi.

07:19.936 --> 07:21.056
In the court,

07:21.056 --> 07:23.337
everyone knows
you are his right-hand man.

07:24.017 --> 07:26.137
If the Imperial Guard handles this case,

07:26.457 --> 07:27.657
how can you avoid suspicion?

07:29.457 --> 07:32.056
I refuse to hand over his body.

07:32.056 --> 07:32.816
Outrageous!

07:33.017 --> 07:35.416
Marquis Muyang is the one
who quelled the Jing'an rebellion.

07:35.577 --> 07:37.496
The rebels' heads he took are numerous.

07:37.657 --> 07:40.217
How dare you wag your tongue

07:40.217 --> 07:41.496
and make accusations?

07:41.697 --> 07:44.856
Are you intending to use force
here in the capital?

07:44.936 --> 07:46.176
So what?

07:46.616 --> 07:48.856
I must take Yuan Fang's body today.

07:48.856 --> 07:49.657
How dare you!

07:50.176 --> 07:52.416
You're so lawless, causing trouble here!

07:52.537 --> 07:55.176
I will petition His Majesty today
to censure you.

07:57.496 --> 07:58.657
Magistrate Gongshu.

07:59.777 --> 08:03.017
Having worked together
for years, why are you so stern?

08:04.777 --> 08:05.816
General Lu,

08:06.657 --> 08:07.936
both you and Magistrate Gongshu

08:08.856 --> 08:11.256
were cultivated by the Empress Dowager.

08:12.296 --> 08:14.017
Let's talk this matter out.

08:14.017 --> 08:16.777
Petition me then! I don't even care.

08:17.457 --> 08:19.537
You think I wouldn't dare?

08:29.977 --> 08:31.297
That's a lamp newly offered?

08:32.136 --> 08:34.337
Yeah, it's the one
Mrs. Lv offered just now.

08:35.016 --> 08:36.417
The Prince Ding is of noble status.

08:36.496 --> 08:38.937
You may place the lamp
at the most noble position,

08:39.057 --> 08:41.337
so the Emperor Immortal
may see it easily.

08:43.177 --> 08:43.776
No need.

08:44.536 --> 08:46.136
The moderate position is sufficient.

08:46.536 --> 08:49.016
Neither His Highness nor I
seek the highest rank here.

08:49.337 --> 08:50.136
Master,

08:50.577 --> 08:51.536
I wish my mother

08:51.536 --> 08:53.817
longevity and live healthily.

08:58.177 --> 09:00.080
Life's essence came from
the Southern Dipper.

09:23.408 --> 09:24.464
(Mo Xiuyao)

09:27.376 --> 09:29.097
May him peace and safety.

09:36.736 --> 09:37.417
Lord Lv?

09:39.536 --> 09:40.337
Lord Lv Boying?

09:48.376 --> 09:49.496
What did you call him?

09:49.736 --> 09:51.656
Lord Lv Boying, don't you recognize me?

09:57.817 --> 09:59.057
You mistook me for another.

10:00.776 --> 10:01.817
Perhaps I did.

10:02.297 --> 10:03.136
My mistake.

10:13.376 --> 10:14.226
Your Highness.

10:14.704 --> 10:16.496
Are you worried about His Highness?

10:18.656 --> 10:19.256
Qingyu.

10:20.016 --> 10:21.337
Let me tell you a story.

10:22.937 --> 10:24.937
An official in the Bureau of Astronomy
of the previous dynasty

10:25.337 --> 10:26.417
excelled in flattery.

10:26.776 --> 10:28.656
To curry favor with the Empress,

10:28.856 --> 10:31.736
he claimed a tree placed at the west
in a concubine's palace

10:32.097 --> 10:34.697
would invite disaster
for overstepping her bounds.

10:35.776 --> 10:36.736
Then what?

10:37.337 --> 10:40.136
To be safe, the Empress
ordered the tree to be cut down.

10:40.736 --> 10:42.697
Then that official advised again.

10:42.896 --> 10:45.376
That concubine's palace faced west.

10:45.656 --> 10:46.937
That invited calamity.

10:47.337 --> 10:49.417
So no tree should be
planted in the palace.

10:50.016 --> 10:52.577
So her palace lost all tree shade.

10:52.697 --> 10:55.697
I wonder if this concubine was at odds

10:55.977 --> 10:57.337
with the Empress.

10:58.016 --> 11:00.136
You grow sharper by the day.

11:01.217 --> 11:03.136
But that official was short-sighted.

11:03.376 --> 11:05.896
He'd never imagined that concubine

11:05.977 --> 11:07.577
would become the Empress Dowager.

11:07.776 --> 11:08.496
Empress Dowager?

11:11.536 --> 11:12.736
The one who reigns now?

11:12.736 --> 11:15.177
Cowardly people like you
never rise high.

11:16.217 --> 11:19.097
Perhaps he found another way.

11:19.856 --> 11:22.376
Like, changing his name.

11:26.256 --> 11:29.328
(Lv Boying)

11:40.536 --> 11:42.697
I am Gongshu Yang.

11:42.697 --> 11:44.297
Greetings, Your Majesty.

11:44.937 --> 11:45.817
Rise.

11:46.577 --> 11:47.776
Thank you, Your Majesty.

11:53.297 --> 11:55.817
You look troubled. What is it?

11:58.896 --> 11:59.856
Your Majesty,

12:00.536 --> 12:01.776
Military Governor Yuan

12:01.776 --> 12:04.256
was assigned to investigate
the weaponry case in Huaixi.

12:04.496 --> 12:05.217
But

12:05.217 --> 12:07.776
he was found dead
in the capital outskirts.

12:09.016 --> 12:10.097
The evidence mentioned

12:10.097 --> 12:13.177
in his official report has disappeared.

12:14.776 --> 12:17.856
Marquis Muyang's
maternal clan is in Huaixi,

12:18.256 --> 12:19.937
where borders Cangbei.

12:19.937 --> 12:22.977
I believe the weaponry case
must be related to him.

12:23.697 --> 12:24.697
Today, Marquis Muyang

12:24.697 --> 12:27.057
dispatched General Lu Changfu

12:27.057 --> 12:28.784
to forcefully storm
the Jingzhao Prefecture,

12:28.856 --> 12:31.417
seizing the corpse
and snatching case files.

12:32.896 --> 12:37.097
Utter nonsense!

12:44.016 --> 12:46.376
Her Majesty had difficulty in eating.

12:46.656 --> 12:47.496
I

12:47.496 --> 12:50.457
barely managed
to interest Her Majesty in eating.

12:50.736 --> 12:51.856
Magistrate Gongshu,

12:51.856 --> 12:54.136
must you report matters now,

12:54.856 --> 12:56.736
ruining Her Majesty's mood?

12:58.536 --> 13:00.217
I deserve death.

13:00.217 --> 13:01.376
But this matter

13:01.376 --> 13:03.217
truly violates the law.

13:03.376 --> 13:05.896
I must report it.

13:07.057 --> 13:08.817
I know of this matter.

13:09.337 --> 13:10.297
Rise.

13:10.896 --> 13:12.856
You Majesty, you're wise.

13:22.536 --> 13:23.577
Anything else?

13:27.016 --> 13:29.337
I have an interesting tale

13:29.337 --> 13:31.337
to tell you.

13:32.376 --> 13:33.376
Recently,

13:33.376 --> 13:35.656
Jingzhao Prefecture
accepted a peculiar case.

13:36.057 --> 13:38.736
The imperial plaque of Family of Charity
for the Ye family

13:38.856 --> 13:39.977
has vanished.

13:40.217 --> 13:43.337
It's a dreadfully unlucky affair
that could cost life!

13:43.616 --> 13:44.616
And then?

13:45.577 --> 13:47.937
Then that plaque

13:47.937 --> 13:50.457
mysteriously emerged from the water.

13:52.697 --> 13:53.736
They claimed

13:53.937 --> 13:56.057
it was hauled from their pond.

13:56.896 --> 13:59.177
It might be the Dragon King

13:59.177 --> 14:00.736
borrowing it as a mirror

14:00.856 --> 14:02.736
and then returning it after use.

14:04.177 --> 14:05.097
Today,

14:05.097 --> 14:08.496
the Ye family sent someone bearing gifts

14:08.496 --> 14:10.536
to Jingzhao Prefecture to thank us.

14:11.177 --> 14:14.697
Unexpectedly, that person and Lord Lv
turned out to be old acquaintances.

14:14.937 --> 14:16.616
He even addressed Lord Lv

14:16.616 --> 14:17.457
by another name.

14:18.457 --> 14:19.616
What is it?

14:20.136 --> 14:21.417
Lv Boying.

14:29.697 --> 14:30.896
Lv Boying?

14:30.960 --> 14:32.016
(Lv Residence)

14:48.937 --> 14:49.896
Let go!

14:49.896 --> 14:50.616
Move!

14:50.697 --> 14:51.577
Let go!

14:52.097 --> 14:53.256
Why arrest me?

14:54.416 --> 14:56.848
(Shunxi)

14:59.337 --> 15:00.240
A misunderstanding.

15:00.937 --> 15:03.656
Eunuch Shunxi! A misunderstanding.

15:06.656 --> 15:07.457
A misunderstanding?

15:09.536 --> 15:10.297
Take him away.

15:10.656 --> 15:11.376
- Yes!
- Yes!

15:11.376 --> 15:12.937
Eunuch Shunxi, a misunderstanding.

15:12.937 --> 15:14.616
Eunuch Shunxi, a misunderstanding!

15:14.616 --> 15:15.337
Eunuch Shunxi!

15:15.440 --> 15:19.120
(Pavilion under Moonlight)

15:22.896 --> 15:24.784
(Lv Cheng has fallen)

15:36.177 --> 15:37.516
(Zhou Jing, Marquis Muyang)
Marquis Muyang,

15:37.516 --> 15:38.856
(Minister of Imperial Court of Judicial Review)
Her Majesty lets you in.

15:42.577 --> 15:43.457
Your Majesty.

15:44.256 --> 15:45.656
I failed in oversight,

15:45.736 --> 15:47.256
ignorant of Lv Cheng's past deeds.

15:47.736 --> 15:49.817
I beg your forgiveness.

15:50.697 --> 15:52.977
Gongshu Yang came yesterday,

15:53.616 --> 15:55.217
wishing to resign and retire.

15:57.177 --> 15:58.457
To pressure a typically

15:58.577 --> 16:00.417
unhurried scholar

16:00.417 --> 16:01.896
to such extremity

16:02.177 --> 16:03.496
was no small feat.

16:05.536 --> 16:07.856
I wonder why Magistrate Gongshu

16:07.896 --> 16:09.057
acted so.

16:09.496 --> 16:10.417
Why?

16:11.297 --> 16:12.337
Don't you know?

16:12.736 --> 16:13.337
Don't tell me

16:14.217 --> 16:16.217
you truly killed Yuan Fang?

16:17.097 --> 16:20.016
Your Majesty, I have absolutely
nothing to do with this matter.

16:20.256 --> 16:22.016
I must be framed!

16:22.856 --> 16:24.736
Your Majesty, I implore
for clear discernment.

16:25.656 --> 16:28.784
Huaixi smuggled blades and crossbows
to enemy nation Cangbei,

16:28.784 --> 16:30.016
shocking court and populace!

16:30.457 --> 16:31.427
Yuan Fang's mission

16:31.427 --> 16:33.937
was to uncover the mastermind behind it.

16:34.217 --> 16:36.256
Yet as a Military Governor of Huaixi,

16:36.376 --> 16:38.256
he was abducted by bandits

16:38.256 --> 16:39.856
and killed in the capital outskirts.

16:41.136 --> 16:44.057
Your Zhou family's roots
in Huaixi run deep.

16:44.736 --> 16:47.136
Then your men forcibly entered
the Jingzhao Prefecture,

16:47.217 --> 16:48.097
seizing case files.

16:48.536 --> 16:51.057
Gongshu Yang's suspicion
of you is justified.

16:52.256 --> 16:54.457
Your Majesty.
Gongshu Yang suspects me...

16:54.457 --> 16:54.977
Enough!

16:55.817 --> 16:59.336
The Imperial Court of Judicial Review
will no longer be involved in this case.

16:59.857 --> 17:00.657
Rise.

17:03.256 --> 17:03.857
Yes.

17:06.617 --> 17:07.657
As for Lv Cheng,

17:08.937 --> 17:10.417
such a vile scoundrel

17:10.897 --> 17:13.496
managed to infiltrate your faction,

17:13.857 --> 17:15.056
stirring up trouble.

17:15.296 --> 17:16.016
It shows

17:16.617 --> 17:17.584
most in your faction

17:17.897 --> 17:19.937
are vile and sinister people.

17:20.256 --> 17:23.657
Can you even tell good from bad?

17:24.857 --> 17:25.657
I am

17:26.736 --> 17:28.096
not discerning.

17:44.857 --> 17:45.897
When did you get here?

17:47.657 --> 17:48.857
While you were talking,

17:48.857 --> 17:51.177
I slipped inside to rest a bit.

17:54.480 --> 17:57.016
(Qin Zheng, Dowager Consort)

17:57.016 --> 17:58.256
It's the drumfish pancakes

17:58.256 --> 18:00.177
freshly bought
by the Imperial Kitchen, right?

18:00.256 --> 18:02.776
They look delicious. Have some?

18:04.256 --> 18:05.217
No appetite.

18:05.977 --> 18:06.857
Why?

18:07.977 --> 18:09.217
Is it because of Marquis Muyang

18:09.872 --> 18:11.056
or His Majesty?

18:18.536 --> 18:20.377
I heard you

18:20.657 --> 18:22.544
punished a servant
from the Imperial Study.

18:22.617 --> 18:23.697
Was it because of your son?

18:26.096 --> 18:28.256
He treated the Imperial Study
like a gambling den.

18:28.377 --> 18:29.617
And I caught him.

18:30.496 --> 18:32.137
He's barely reached adulthood,

18:32.417 --> 18:33.857
still immature, impulsive,

18:33.857 --> 18:35.377
and naughty.

18:36.096 --> 18:38.177
A boy of his age isn't young anymore.

18:39.096 --> 18:42.177
Soon, he'll reign the nation.

18:43.776 --> 18:46.137
Your excellent ability
reigns the nation well.

18:46.296 --> 18:47.956
You might as well

18:47.956 --> 18:49.417
reign for a few more years.

18:53.936 --> 18:56.998
(Prison of Imperial Court
of Judicial Review)

19:02.697 --> 19:03.856
I demand to see the Marquis Muyang!

19:04.337 --> 19:05.736
I demand to see the Marquis Muyang!

19:07.096 --> 19:08.336
I demand to see the Marquis Muyang!

19:08.496 --> 19:10.736
I demand to see the Marquis Muyang!

19:13.217 --> 19:14.336
I demand to see the Marquis Muyang!

19:16.657 --> 19:18.657
Marquis Muyang!

19:19.296 --> 19:20.897
Marquis Muyang, punish me!

19:21.177 --> 19:22.576
No. I deserve to die!

19:22.857 --> 19:25.016
I was so reckless years ago,

19:25.016 --> 19:26.417
and offended the Empress Dowager.

19:26.417 --> 19:28.256
Save me, Marquis Muyang!

19:32.256 --> 19:34.177
At least you remember whom you offended.

19:34.617 --> 19:35.496
For years,

19:35.736 --> 19:37.137
you've been hiding in my faction.

19:37.137 --> 19:38.417
Tell me, what are you plotting?

19:40.576 --> 19:42.377
Want to get me killed?

19:51.056 --> 19:52.137
Take him away.

19:52.496 --> 19:53.137
Yes.

19:53.137 --> 19:53.744
Marquis Muyang.

19:53.808 --> 19:54.496
Marquis Muyang.

19:54.496 --> 19:55.736
- Get up.
- Save me!

19:55.856 --> 19:56.496
Marquis Muyang!

19:56.496 --> 19:57.217
Let's go.

19:57.217 --> 19:58.296
Save me, Marquis Muyang!

19:58.296 --> 19:58.897
Hurry.

19:58.897 --> 19:59.657
Marquis Muyang!

20:00.177 --> 20:01.457
Save me, Marquis Muyang!

20:01.897 --> 20:02.697
Marquis Muyang!

20:03.657 --> 20:04.336
Yaoguang Palace.

20:04.697 --> 20:05.377
I won't go in.

20:05.377 --> 20:06.256
- Go.
- I won't!

20:06.256 --> 20:06.816
Go.

20:06.816 --> 20:07.657
- Go.
- I won't!

20:08.336 --> 20:09.056
Marquis Muyang!

20:09.056 --> 20:09.576
Go!

20:09.576 --> 20:10.857
Save me, Marquis Muyang!

20:11.096 --> 20:12.016
I won't go in!

20:12.496 --> 20:13.256
Marquis Muyang!

20:13.697 --> 20:14.536
Marquis Muyang!

20:14.536 --> 20:15.016
(Yaoguang Palace)

20:15.016 --> 20:16.296
Marquis Muyang!

20:24.336 --> 20:26.776
I wonder why you summon me,
Marquis Muyang?

20:28.937 --> 20:30.096
He broke the law.

20:30.736 --> 20:32.977
I intend to punish him.

20:34.496 --> 20:36.617
So I need you as witness.

20:37.617 --> 20:39.617
I-I was so blind.

20:39.977 --> 20:41.857
Please spare me, Empress Dowager!

20:43.217 --> 20:43.857
Eunuch Shunxi!

20:45.377 --> 20:46.897
Please save me.

20:47.096 --> 20:48.336
Plead for me.

20:48.336 --> 20:49.576
Please save me.

20:52.897 --> 20:54.536
Now you fear?

20:54.697 --> 20:56.977
When you cut down the ancient cedar
at Yaoguang Palace,

20:57.377 --> 20:58.857
you scried the stars

20:58.977 --> 21:00.377
and claimed divine mandate.

21:03.897 --> 21:06.377
The Yaoguang Palace is two gates
and three corridors away

21:06.576 --> 21:09.056
from the Zichen Palace.

21:10.417 --> 21:12.256
Back then,
the Empress Dowager lived here.

21:12.736 --> 21:14.776
Only fetching water took one hour.

21:15.617 --> 21:16.576
The oil for lamps

21:16.897 --> 21:19.256
collected drop by drop
from the Palace Domestic Service.

21:19.736 --> 21:21.977
The Empress Dowager is compassionate.

21:23.016 --> 21:25.617
She always copied sutras
beneath the ancient tree,

21:25.937 --> 21:27.457
blessing the people.

21:27.897 --> 21:29.496
It is truly a blessing for our dynasty.

21:32.417 --> 21:33.657
Who would've thought

21:34.897 --> 21:37.016
such an auspicious tree
in Yaoguang Palace

21:37.496 --> 21:39.736
would be destroyed by you?

21:39.760 --> 21:40.464
Tree!

21:40.576 --> 21:41.096
Tree!

21:41.617 --> 21:42.137
Tree!

21:42.256 --> 21:43.016
Tree!

21:43.016 --> 21:44.417
I'll plant a new tree!

21:45.016 --> 21:47.576
J-Just plant one exactly like before.

21:48.056 --> 21:48.857
I...

21:48.857 --> 21:49.576
No.

21:49.697 --> 21:51.336
One more lush than the previous one.

21:51.417 --> 21:52.857
More lush than the previous one.

21:58.377 --> 21:59.496
In that case,

22:00.697 --> 22:01.576
go ahead and plant it.

22:03.217 --> 22:05.457
Make sure it's more lush
than the previous one.

22:06.576 --> 22:07.256
Marquis Muyang.

22:07.457 --> 22:08.137
Marquis Muyang.

22:08.576 --> 22:09.296
Marquis Muyang.

22:09.417 --> 22:10.096
Marquis Muyang.

22:10.217 --> 22:11.536
Marquis Muyang!

23:10.256 --> 23:10.857
Who's there?

24:24.417 --> 24:26.377
Your Highness, what are you looking at?

24:27.657 --> 24:29.177
Nothing. Let's head back.

24:29.392 --> 24:29.977
Okay.

24:57.296 --> 24:58.160
What are you doing?

24:59.256 --> 25:00.144
Delivering a letter.

25:03.016 --> 25:04.144
What are you looking at?

25:04.417 --> 25:06.096
Go get me a cloth to wipe this off.

25:18.217 --> 25:19.137
If you love water,

25:19.736 --> 25:22.016
I'll have someone
build you a pond another day.

25:22.377 --> 25:23.336
(Feng Zhiyao)
No need.

25:23.377 --> 25:24.736
(Head of Qingfeng Mingyue Tower)
Your residence already has one.

25:24.776 --> 25:26.457
Well, blame your Princess Consort.

25:26.457 --> 25:28.897
Her eyes are too sharp.
She spotted me in an instant.

25:29.457 --> 25:32.217
Luckily, I know some tricks
to vanish into thin air.

25:32.256 --> 25:33.496
That's how I escaped.

25:34.576 --> 25:36.377
Alright, let's get down to business.

25:36.697 --> 25:38.776
Lv Cheng has fallen.

25:43.177 --> 25:44.577
The current Lv Boying

25:44.752 --> 25:46.217
becomes a small sapling.

25:46.937 --> 25:48.457
Take your hand off.

25:51.977 --> 25:53.016
So, Your Highness,

25:53.417 --> 25:55.977
you see how adept
he is at playing both sides?

25:56.217 --> 25:57.816
To curry favor with the Empress,

25:57.977 --> 25:59.496
he cut down Consort Guo's shade tree.

26:00.177 --> 26:01.536
When Consort Guo gained power,

26:01.617 --> 26:03.217
he then fled far away to Lianzhou.

26:03.296 --> 26:05.657
Serving in Lianzhou,
he changed his name.

26:05.816 --> 26:07.697
Later, during
a report-back to the capital,

26:07.816 --> 26:10.096
he found a way
to latch onto Marquis Muyang.

26:10.177 --> 26:11.657
This man is utterly heartless,

26:11.736 --> 26:12.897
arrogant and overbearing.

26:13.457 --> 26:16.016
Who'd have thought
he'd stumble over a guard?

26:17.936 --> 26:18.672
Right.

26:21.296 --> 26:23.617
Earlier, while coming over,
I scraped against your wall.

26:24.217 --> 26:25.016
Pay for that.

26:28.457 --> 26:28.977
No.

26:30.697 --> 26:31.496
What a stingy man.

26:31.857 --> 26:33.336
What a stingy man you are.

26:33.457 --> 26:36.137
You should act more mature now.
Come through the door.

26:36.496 --> 26:37.137
No way.

26:37.617 --> 26:38.776
If a secret agent

26:39.377 --> 26:41.816
isn't using the walls,
it is not mysterious enough.

26:54.217 --> 26:56.176
(I heard it's a guard of Ye Mansion
who exposed)

26:56.697 --> 26:58.336
(Lv Cheng's real name.)

27:11.016 --> 27:11.657
Your Highness.

27:18.776 --> 27:19.736
Perfect timing.

27:20.937 --> 27:23.296
The kitchen made lotus cakes for me,
and they're still warm.

27:23.617 --> 27:24.336
Want a bite?

27:27.857 --> 27:28.697
What did you step on?

27:28.977 --> 27:29.617
Nothing.

27:30.576 --> 27:31.457
Eat some cakes.

27:34.296 --> 27:36.576
Lift your foot up and let me see.

27:38.336 --> 27:39.296
It really is nothing.

27:41.736 --> 27:42.536
Lift your foot up.

27:52.176 --> 27:53.680
(Lv Cheng)

27:57.937 --> 27:58.736
Lv Cheng?

28:01.496 --> 28:04.056
He's not a good man. I hate him.

28:04.816 --> 28:06.177
But I can't do anything about him,

28:06.697 --> 28:09.217
so I can only use
this folk trick against him.

28:10.096 --> 28:11.096
It's called Stepping On Villains.

28:11.776 --> 28:14.496
Just step on the name
of the person you resent,

28:14.857 --> 28:15.937
and it'll make him unlucky.

28:16.897 --> 28:19.776
I know it's harmful to harmony.

28:20.256 --> 28:21.056
I shouldn't do it.

28:22.016 --> 28:23.776
But Lv Cheng is truly detestable!

28:26.816 --> 28:27.977
Why do so?

28:29.857 --> 28:32.736
This scoundrel dares to bully you.

28:33.256 --> 28:34.857
As your Princess Consort,

28:34.977 --> 28:36.536
I have to get revenge for you.

28:42.217 --> 28:43.137
By using this trick?

28:46.016 --> 28:47.736
Don't underestimate it.

28:48.177 --> 28:50.336
I learned this from an ancient book.

28:50.496 --> 28:51.857
They say it's very efficacious.

28:52.256 --> 28:53.697
Back when Duke Zheng attacked Xu,

28:53.697 --> 28:55.897
to punish the one
who assassinated Ying Kaoshu,

28:56.056 --> 28:58.937
they used this very method against him.

28:59.657 --> 29:00.736
Rest assured.

29:00.816 --> 29:03.217
Within three days,
he will surely fall gravely ill.

29:03.920 --> 29:05.096
(Lv Cheng)

29:05.096 --> 29:06.336
Don't do such things anymore.

29:13.096 --> 29:15.496
Seems the Princess Consort
really isn't simple.

29:16.536 --> 29:17.657
How?

29:18.056 --> 29:20.096
She's quite studied in such tricks.

29:21.137 --> 29:22.617
She even read my fortune for me.

29:23.217 --> 29:23.776
Really?

29:27.897 --> 29:29.296
I understand, Your Highness.

29:30.697 --> 29:31.897
Lv Cheng's falling

29:31.977 --> 29:33.816
must be because of this trick!

29:42.296 --> 29:44.617
Where's your brain?
Did you leave it in her room?

29:46.897 --> 29:49.657
Your Highness, do you think

29:49.776 --> 29:52.016
that Lv Cheng's death is related
to the Princess Consort?

29:53.977 --> 29:55.177
But to me,

29:55.496 --> 29:57.296
the Princess Consort seems very innocent

29:57.736 --> 29:58.736
and genuinely kind.

30:00.857 --> 30:02.672
Your Highness, this is the congee
improved by Princess Consort

30:02.672 --> 30:04.937
and she told me to deliver to you daily.

30:05.256 --> 30:06.256
Will you take it now?

30:12.304 --> 30:15.472
(Marquis Muyang's Residence)

30:16.697 --> 30:17.527
All these years,

30:18.096 --> 30:19.736
you've received my support.

30:20.496 --> 30:23.857
Have I ever mistreated
any of you in the slightest?

30:25.736 --> 30:28.336
If anyone dares
to hide something from me again,

30:29.336 --> 30:31.336
do not blame me for showing no mercy.

30:32.857 --> 30:35.496
We dare not forget your great kindness.

30:35.617 --> 30:36.736
- Never dare to forget.
- Never dare to forget.

30:38.417 --> 30:40.937
Marquis Muyang,
you visited the palace yesterday.

30:40.937 --> 30:41.177
(Zhang Hengyuan, Maritime Trade Officer)

30:41.177 --> 30:42.977
May I know what the Empress Dowager say?

30:45.697 --> 30:46.736
Lv Cheng doesn't matter.

30:47.496 --> 30:48.336
What matters is

30:48.897 --> 30:51.816
that the case of Yuan Fang is now
handled by the Jingzhao Prefecture.

30:51.977 --> 30:53.657
It must be Gongshu Yang's scheme.

30:54.617 --> 30:55.776
Then, Marquis Muyang,

30:55.897 --> 30:57.857
what should we do now?

30:58.016 --> 31:00.736
Yuan Fang's death
was not our doing regardless.

31:01.816 --> 31:04.096
Gongshu Yang is an upright minister,

31:04.736 --> 31:06.256
and he wouldn't stoop to framing.

31:07.736 --> 31:08.897
The important matter now

31:09.937 --> 31:11.137
is Huaixi.

31:11.576 --> 31:13.617
You are right.

31:14.137 --> 31:16.177
Yuan Fang died just at the right time.

31:16.576 --> 31:18.377
The Huaixi affair has alarmed the court.

31:18.377 --> 31:20.857
We must not let the Imperial Court
place their people again.

31:20.897 --> 31:23.816
We must have our own people in control.

31:24.857 --> 31:25.937
I have my plan.

31:26.977 --> 31:28.016
Everyone, leave.

31:28.377 --> 31:29.177
Yes.

31:34.977 --> 31:35.576
Changfu.

31:39.496 --> 31:40.056
You stay.

32:17.377 --> 32:18.417
Your Highness, what brings you here?

32:21.256 --> 32:22.137
Just passing by.

32:24.776 --> 32:25.657
Writing a letter?

32:29.616 --> 32:30.256
Yes.

32:30.657 --> 32:31.937
I'm writing to my grandfather,

32:32.417 --> 32:34.816
my teachers, and the senior brothers
from Lishan Mountain.

32:37.016 --> 32:38.776
It's been a long while since I saw them.

32:39.576 --> 32:41.697
They all must be missing me.

32:43.217 --> 32:45.657
Your Highnesses, the congee is ready.

33:11.417 --> 33:13.377
Why did you add honey to the congee?

33:13.816 --> 33:15.256
Shouldn't it be savory?

33:15.617 --> 33:17.977
Savory or sweet one,
each has its merits.

33:19.377 --> 33:22.377
On the mountain, there wasn't much
to eat. Every meal was millet congee.

33:23.096 --> 33:25.377
Teachers preferred savory congee,

33:25.816 --> 33:28.137
with pickles for flavor.

33:29.256 --> 33:32.137
But Master Zhu was different.
He liked it sweet,

33:33.056 --> 33:35.137
and would secretly add honey,

33:35.617 --> 33:37.937
then tell us it was just salt water.

33:38.496 --> 33:39.697
I learned it from him.

33:40.457 --> 33:41.457
You seem

33:42.256 --> 33:43.857
to miss the life on the mountain.

33:47.736 --> 33:49.336
Are you going to send me away again?

34:04.897 --> 34:06.937
But Prince Ding

34:07.777 --> 34:11.536
is quite...

34:16.176 --> 34:17.737
How could you peek at my letter?

34:17.977 --> 34:19.576
Your letter is right there.

34:20.216 --> 34:21.656
I just take a look.

34:23.337 --> 34:24.576
Anyway, you can't read it.

34:25.257 --> 34:27.656
Qingyu, prepare some congee
for His Highness as well.

34:28.056 --> 34:28.752
Yes.

34:28.897 --> 34:31.016
Then I'll go help.

34:39.216 --> 34:41.817
You look quite comfortable here,

34:41.977 --> 34:43.777
coming and going freely.

34:43.937 --> 34:46.337
Of course, here is my home.

34:52.616 --> 34:53.897
Since I married you,

34:54.777 --> 34:56.656
I wish to build a good life with you.

34:57.176 --> 35:00.056
You just don't
understand me very well yet.

35:01.016 --> 35:01.897
It's alright.

35:02.257 --> 35:04.897
Over time, we'll naturally become close.

35:05.937 --> 35:08.216
I haven't consummated
the marriage with you,

35:08.536 --> 35:11.257
and perhaps it suits your wishes.

35:23.457 --> 35:23.977
Look,

35:24.656 --> 35:27.056
this little spider
is good at weaving webs.

35:27.737 --> 35:29.737
Because the shape of its web

35:30.216 --> 35:32.096
resembles eight trigrams of I Ching,

35:32.696 --> 35:34.337
and it likes to eat harmful insects.

35:34.817 --> 35:36.216
Usually, wherever it appears,

35:36.297 --> 35:38.056
crops grow better.

35:38.417 --> 35:39.888
So villagers below the mountain

35:39.888 --> 35:41.777
usually call it a Lucky Spider,

35:42.096 --> 35:44.496
believing it'd bring someone good luck.

35:46.417 --> 35:48.576
Your Highness, you'll have good luck.

36:07.216 --> 36:10.016
Excuse me, could you let
this elder gentleman pass first?

36:10.536 --> 36:11.096
Alright.

36:11.536 --> 36:14.096
Sir, wrong way, this way.

36:14.937 --> 36:15.897
This way.

36:23.176 --> 36:24.056
My lady,

36:24.656 --> 36:26.737
Prince Ding seems displeased with us.

36:28.536 --> 36:30.257
But some things must be done.

36:31.056 --> 36:33.337
Do you miss the life on the mountain?

36:35.616 --> 36:36.417
I do,

36:37.536 --> 36:38.897
but I don't wish to return.

36:39.937 --> 36:41.377
The mountain is too quiet.

36:41.777 --> 36:43.377
It makes me feel terribly alone.

36:44.536 --> 36:45.937
But down here, it's different.

36:46.457 --> 36:49.457
It's vibrant, bustling,
and packed with people.

36:50.176 --> 36:51.344
Even if I do nothing,

36:51.696 --> 36:53.297
just sitting here

36:53.777 --> 36:56.136
and watching the pedestrians
rushing back and forth

36:56.457 --> 36:57.977
is fascinating.

36:58.777 --> 37:00.377
Why are you watching them?

37:00.737 --> 37:04.257
They all seem the same.

37:04.737 --> 37:05.696
Not at all.

37:06.777 --> 37:09.337
Each person
has their own distinct scent.

37:09.457 --> 37:11.457
By smelling their scent,

37:11.536 --> 37:13.056
I can see many things about them.

37:16.417 --> 37:18.616
Then, what's Prince Ding's scent?

37:22.897 --> 37:23.696
I don't know.

37:25.176 --> 37:26.536
He's like being in water,

37:27.096 --> 37:28.696
with his scent isolated.

37:29.457 --> 37:30.457
I can't smell it.

37:34.937 --> 37:36.016
(Cover the Young General!)

37:36.136 --> 37:37.897
(Go! Go now!)

37:38.056 --> 37:39.216
(Criminal official Mo Xiuwen)

37:39.737 --> 37:42.216
(returned to the capital
without imperial decree,)

37:42.777 --> 37:45.496
(causing the border defenses to fall,
and the land being seized by Cangbei.)

37:46.176 --> 37:48.496
(Tens of thousands of soldiers
and civilians perished,)

37:48.616 --> 37:49.737
(bringing disaster to the border.)

37:50.417 --> 37:52.112
(Therefore, charged with treason,)

37:52.656 --> 37:54.016
(he is beheaded as execution.)

37:54.737 --> 37:56.377
(My brother would never
return without an imperial decree.)

37:56.977 --> 37:59.257
(Imperial decree!
There must be an imperial decree!)

38:00.377 --> 38:03.297
(The imperial decree? I burned it.)

38:10.817 --> 38:12.937
The Empress Dowager
resents Marquis Muyang,

38:13.136 --> 38:14.656
but Lv Cheng is merely a small fry.

38:14.777 --> 38:15.937
She just wanted to vent her anger.

38:16.897 --> 38:18.576
Marquis Muyang has been
manipulating things for days.

38:18.576 --> 38:20.176
It is expected that in court today,

38:20.176 --> 38:22.777
he will nominate Lu Changfu
as the Military Governor of Huaixi.

38:22.937 --> 38:24.417
After that, dragging him down

38:24.417 --> 38:26.096
will be more difficult.

38:29.216 --> 38:31.857
Huaixi is the vital heartland
of our dynasty,

38:32.056 --> 38:33.777
the shield protecting
the Jianghuai region.

38:33.897 --> 38:35.496
The post of Military Governor of Huaixi

38:35.496 --> 38:37.616
is crucial and cannot remain vacant.

38:38.257 --> 38:39.737
I nominate

38:39.737 --> 38:43.016
General of the Imperial Guard,
Lu Changfu, for the position.

38:46.616 --> 38:47.897
What do you think,
Chief Imperial Secretary?

38:50.176 --> 38:52.616
Your Majesty, I find this improper.

38:53.056 --> 38:55.297
(Murong Shen, Chief Imperial Secretary)
General Lu could safeguard the palace,

38:55.656 --> 38:58.176
but the situation in Huaixi
might be too complex for him.

38:59.096 --> 38:59.897
Your Majesty.

39:00.897 --> 39:03.377
General Lu is meticulous and steady.

39:04.977 --> 39:07.176
If he's as Military Governor of Huaixi,

39:07.616 --> 39:10.696
he will be certain to handle
Huaixi's military affairs well.

39:11.176 --> 39:12.112
In five days,

39:12.496 --> 39:14.257
head to Huaixi to take up your post.

39:18.977 --> 39:20.136
Thank you, Your Majesty.

39:20.297 --> 39:23.897
I shall not fail your grace.

39:25.536 --> 39:27.297
Your Majesty, you are wise.

39:33.072 --> 39:35.440
(Duke Hua)

40:03.377 --> 40:05.096
Your Highness, everything is packed.

40:05.417 --> 40:06.216
Let's go.

40:12.616 --> 40:14.016
Your Highness, give it to me.

40:14.257 --> 40:15.457
Here. Thank you.

40:26.096 --> 40:26.897
Sister-in-law.

40:28.257 --> 40:29.377
Where have you gone?

40:31.737 --> 40:33.536
She has been unwell recently.

40:33.656 --> 40:36.576
Hearing that Zheng Jiuzhen returned
to the capital, she went to visit

40:36.616 --> 40:37.897
to take care of her health.

40:38.737 --> 40:39.897
What did the physician say?

40:40.297 --> 40:42.457
I know some acupuncture as well.

40:42.817 --> 40:45.576
I feel much better already.
Thank you for your concern.

41:03.656 --> 41:04.656
Your Highness.

41:04.817 --> 41:05.656
Where's His Highness?

41:06.056 --> 41:08.696
His Highness is still in the study.

41:09.257 --> 41:10.337
Hasn't he come out?

41:10.337 --> 41:11.016
No.

41:15.792 --> 41:21.360
(Mo Xiuwen, Mo Xiuyao,
Sentenced to the sword and imprisoned)

41:32.528 --> 41:33.977
(Vigilant From Dawn to Dusk)

41:33.977 --> 41:36.216
Your Highness, what brings you here?

41:37.056 --> 41:38.176
His Highness is inside?

41:40.136 --> 41:41.176
He hasn't eaten all day?

41:42.536 --> 41:43.337
He hasn't eaten.

41:44.616 --> 41:46.457
Don't you go in and check on him?

41:46.977 --> 41:49.136
We were forbidden to enter
while Lv Cheng was present.

41:49.136 --> 41:50.457
And now, what's the reason?

41:53.656 --> 41:54.457
Your Highness,

41:55.377 --> 41:58.056
His Highness ordered
that no one may enter.

41:59.136 --> 41:59.937
Move!

42:02.297 --> 42:03.096
Ding!

42:04.136 --> 42:04.977
Your Highness,

42:05.496 --> 42:08.377
His Highness did give orders.

42:08.857 --> 42:10.377
If you insist on barging in,

42:10.377 --> 42:11.897
His Highness will be furious.

42:13.536 --> 42:14.337
Your Highness.

42:14.576 --> 42:15.536
Move aside!

42:15.536 --> 42:17.377
If you don't move, I'll bite you.

42:17.536 --> 42:20.257
Please don't put me
in a difficult position.

42:22.737 --> 42:24.737
Mo Xiuyao, come out!

42:34.937 --> 42:36.216
Go prepare some food

42:36.897 --> 42:38.136
and send it in to His Highness.

42:38.737 --> 42:39.536
Yes.

42:40.912 --> 42:43.824
(Preview)

42:44.297 --> 42:46.696
(If Lu Changfu succeeds
as Military Governor of Huaixi,)

42:46.897 --> 42:48.777
(taking Marquis Muyang down
will be hard.)

42:48.777 --> 42:50.136
(Since His Majesty desires this,)

42:50.616 --> 42:52.777
(Li, let us proceed accordingly.)

42:53.737 --> 42:54.817
(One more thing.)

42:55.096 --> 42:58.056
(I found Wei Zhuang,
but I dared not reveal myself to him.)

43:01.536 --> 43:02.417
Mo Xiuyao,

43:03.536 --> 43:04.977
don't let your life

43:05.817 --> 43:07.817
become a show in their eyes.

43:15.577 --> 43:22.169
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.753 --> 43:31.897
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.105 --> 43:37.337
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.561 --> 43:43.577
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:43.897 --> 43:47.321
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.385 --> 43:53.945
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.001 --> 43:58.937
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:58.937 --> 44:04.633
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.145 --> 44:13.753
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.649 --> 44:20.153
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.153 --> 44:25.657
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.721 --> 44:29.785
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.073 --> 44:35.297
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:35.897 --> 44:39.609
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.641 --> 44:45.305
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.073 --> 44:54.041
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.449 --> 45:00.697
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:00.953 --> 45:06.857
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:06.857 --> 45:10.977
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.193 --> 45:15.929
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.145 --> 45:21.417
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.657 --> 45:27.097
♪Unbound by form♪
